platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In this imaginative animated storybook, two of Sesame Streets most popular characters team up to spark your childs love of reading. As fearful Grover concocts hilarious obstacles to keep kids from reaching the last page, eager Elmo asks for their help to discover the mysterious monster at the end of the story. Its an engaging experience that teaches bravery and conflict resolution through lively interactivity, adorable artwork, and heartwarming humor. Parental tips help you integrate these lessons during storytime and beyond, combining learning and play with practical advice from a name you can trust.
